;}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1744:\"<p>The long-awaited release of WordPress 3.3 is now available! You can download <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/2011/12/sonny/\">&#8220;Sonny&#8221;</a>, the latest WordPress software version, directly from <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/download/\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress.org</a>, or from within your dashboard after logging into your site. <strong>But before you upgrade, make sure you have a full backup of your site</strong>. While updates usually run smoothly, it&#8217;s still possible that you could experience a data loss.</p>\n<p>Make sure you have <a href=\"http://pluginbuddy.com/purchase/backupbuddy/\">BackupBuddy</a>&#8211;the easiest, fastest way to create a confidence-inspiring backup. Remember, BackupBuddy makes a <em>complete</em> backup of your entire WordPress install (widgets, themes, plugins, and SQL database &#8211; the entire package).</p>\n<p>New to BackupBuddy? In this video, we guide you through creating your first backup:</p>\n<div id=\"pb-vidembed-c1\" class=\"pb-vidembed-container\"><h4>Getting Started with BackupBuddy</h4><embed src=\"http://vimeo.com/moogaloop.swf?clip_id=31096665&amp;server=vimeo.com&amp;show_title=hide&amp;show_byline=hide&amp;show_portrait=hide&amp;color=00ADEF&amp;fullscreen=1&amp;autoplay=0&amp;loop=0\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" width=\"480\" height=\"300\" wmode=\"opaque\"></embed></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Curious of the new version features? Join us tomorrow during iThemes TV for a complete <a href=\"http://webdesign.com/wordpress/wordpress-3-3-is-out-the-door/\">WordPress 3.3 walk-through</a> and read <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/2011/12/sonny/\">WordPress 3.3&#8242;s release announcement</a>.</p>\n<!-- PHP 5.x -->\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36