ide the desired functionality for their website.</p>\n<p>To be the 2012 Recommended Web Tool means that the WebHostingSearch Team are convinced that WebsiteDefender is one of the most valuable tools to help ensure your website security. A few features of WebsiteDefender are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>In-depth security checks for malware.</li>\n<li>Regular monitoring for under the hood hacker activity.</li>\n<li>Automated Backups and easy restoration.</li>\n<li>Alerts if important files are modified pointing to hacker activity (<a title=\"Check Your File Integrity Validation\" href=\"http://www.websitedefender.com/web-security/file-integrity-validation-security-check/\">file integrity validation</a>).</li>\n<li>Email notifications in case of any malware, hacker activity or vulnerabilities detected on your website.</li>\n<li>The <a title=\"WebsiteDefender WordPress Security plugin\" href=\"http://www.websitedefender.com/websitedefender-wordpress-security-plugin/\">WebsiteDefender WordPress Security plugin</a> that works in tandem with the WebsiteDefender service to offer extra protection for WordPress websites.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>View the WebHostingSearch <a title=\"WebHostingSearch Recommendation for WebsiteDefender \" href=\"http://www.webhostingsearch.com/WebsiteDefender\" target=\"_blank\">recommendation for WebsiteDefender here</a>.</p>\n<p><a title=\"WebsiteDefender Registration Page\" href=\"https://dashboard.websitedefender.com/register-for-free-website-scan.php\">Sign up for your WebsiteDefender account here</a> to see for yourself why it comes highly recommended by WebHostingSearch.com.</p>\n<p>Stay up to date with the latest information about the web security world by ‘liking’ our <a title=\"WebsiteDefender Facebook Page\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/WebsiteDefender\" target=\"_blank\">WebsiteDefender Facebook Page</a> and reading our <a title=\"WebsiteDefender Blog\" href=\"http://www.websitedefender.com/blog/\">WebsiteDefender Blog</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{